# Installation

## From Source

```
git clone https://github.com/thesimonharms/jaringan
cd jaringan
cargo build --release
cp target/release/jaringan-browser ~/.local/bin/
```

## Prerequisites

- Rust 1.96+ (edition 2024)
- cargo

## Verify

```
jaringan-browser open .
```

